title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Shut Up and Scribble Pt. II with Saeed Ferguson
description:
*Record scratch* *freeze frame* Yup, it’s Throwing Fits. You’re probably wondering how the run of show got in this situation. You already know the paradigm stays shifting behind the paywall as this week’s radiant episode continues with ALLCAPSTUDIO’s Saeed Ferguson, who gets more cheese than Doritos, Cheetos or Fritos. Take our hands and join us in spreading peace and love as we discuss the next great generation of streetwear, aging out of the loop, new brand discovery, generational hypebests, butt vs. non-butt sneakers, having laser specific taste and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
